# Fibonacci sequence in Glyph
# Demonstrates pattern matching and recursion

fibonacci:
  [○ n] → [◯ n < 2] ─true─→ [○ 1]
                    └false─→ [▷ add] ← [▷ fibonacci] ← [▷ subtract] ← [○ n] ← [○ 1]
                            ← [▷ fibonacci] ← [▷ subtract] ← [○ n] ← [○ 2]

main:
  [○ 10] → [▷ fibonacci] → [⤶ print]
